<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="#evidence2">
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="#Evidence"/>
  <evidenceContent rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">The Minnesota Vikings has been awarded TRUSTe s Privacy Seal signifying that this privacy policy and practices have been reviewed by TRUSTe for compliance with TRUSTe s program requirements including transparency accountability and choice regarding the collection and use of your personal information The TRUSTe program covers information collected through this Web site www vikings com and www minnesotavikings com and does not cover information that may be collected through our mobile applications TRUSTe s mission as an independent third party is to accelerate online trust among consumers and organizations globally through its leading privacy trustmark and innovative trust solutions If you have questions or complaints regarding our privacy policy or practices please contact us here If you are not satisfied with our response you can contact TRUSTe here</evidenceContent>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

